*Information*
CTF Name: Bandit Level0
Profile: OverTheWire 
Difficulty: Easy
Description: Level 0 aims to teach beginners how to use SSH in order to be able to complete the following challenges.

*Content*
In order to connect through SSH(Secure Shell Protocol), you must open your terminal and use the command ssh bandit0@bandit.labs.overthewire.org -p 2220
                                                                                                         ^      ^               ^                ^   ^
                                                                                                      command   |              host              |  port#
                                                                                                             username                            |
                                                                                                                                      flag to specify port
SSH is used to provide a secure encrypted connection between computers
